                                "#text": "<font color=\"#c5b14d\"><i>\"Our ruler is a man-god, a beacon of light gifted with secrets of creation! His lineage kept our realm safe from the long night for centuries... but now that he disappeared with no descendants, we can only fear the worse for our lands.\"<\/i><\/font>\\n\\n<font size=\"24\" color=\"#c5b14d\"><b>Mah'alam, fifth shield of the Kingless<\/b><\/font>\\n_________________________________________________________   \\n\n<font color=\"#c5b14d\">The kingdom of Laibon has a strong history of assigning their best warriors to the protection of their ruler. Yet, a few decades ago their king disappeared following a series of tragic events. Since then, these warriors became \"The Kingless\", training day and night purposelessly but ever ready to fulfill their oath should the crown return. One of them however chose not to wait any longer: he left the realm to track down clues of his sovereign's whereabouts. Should there be nothing left to protect then he would avenge him, and bring back the crown for a new king to take the throne.<\/font>"
