                                "#text": "Every ailment that stacks which you inflict is also inflicted on you. Each time you reach 10 stacks of one ailment type, that ailment is removed completely, giving you and your allies a bonus for a short time depending on which ailment is removed.\\n\\nIf Stasis stacks were removed, movement speed is increased.\\n\\nIf Cursed stacks were removed, all resistances are increased.\\n\\nIf Weakness stacks were removed, damage is increased.\\n\\nIf any other stacks were removed, Health and Force Shield are regenerated."
