                            "Data": {
                                "@Type": "String",
                                "#text": "Whenever your Willpower is under a certain percentage, each time you use a skill there is a small chance that you will cause an explosion. You and enemies take a percentage of your maximum Health OR Force Shield (whichever is highest) as damage, and a percentage of your Willpower is regenerated.\\n\\nThe element of the damage dealt is selected randomly between Lightning, Fire, and Frost."
                            }
